text: North Chuctanunda Creek flows into the Mohawk River in Amsterdam, New York. Variant names include Chucttonaneda Creek, Jutalaga, North Chaughtanoonda Creek, North Chuctenunda Creek, and Ouctanunda Creek. == References == Category:Rivers of Montgomery County, New York Category:Mohawk River Category:Rivers of New York (state)
title: North Chuctanunda Creek
